Insider Activity


Individual




Richard F. Wallman



Mr. Richard F. Wallman is Independent Director at Extended Stay America, Inc., Independent Director at Charles River Laboratories International, Inc., Independent Director at Convergys Corp., and Independent Director at Roper Technologies, Inc. He is on the Board of Directors at Extended Stay America, Inc., Charles River Laboratories International, Inc., Bausch & Lomb Holdings, Inc., Convergys Corp., Roper Technologies, Inc., Bausch & Lomb, Inc., RMI Corp., Rural/Metro Corp., ESH Hospitality, Inc., Tornier, Inc., and Accriva Diagnostics, Inc.
Mr. Wallman was previously employed as a Member-Managers Board by ESH Hospitality Holdings LLC, a Member-Managers Board by ESH Hospitality Strategies Holdings LLC, Independent Director by Dana Holding Corp., Independent Non-Executive Director by Tornier NV, Independent Director by Ariba, Inc., Chief Financial Officer & Senior Vice President by Allied Signal, Inc., Chief Financial Officer & Senior Vice President by Honeywell International, Inc., a Principal by Chrysler Corp., and Vice President & Controller by International Business Machines Corp. He also served on the board at ExpressJet Holdings, Inc., Hayes Lemmerz International, Inc., Lear Corp., and Avaya, Inc.
He received his undergraduate degree from Vanderbilt University and an MBA from The University of Chicago Booth School of Business.



